name: TAMAGO-CHAN
body:
## About me
My name is Tamara and i'm 13 from Chile, i made this GitHub account to learn to use git and to start making webpages.
I'm currently learning PHP, CSS3, HTML5 and MySQL, i know the basic but i often feel i know nothing at all specially when i see other people's repos

## Current project
I'm currently working on a simple forum project as a method of learning OOP, i'll post updates as i work on it.

## My repos
* [**Hello-World**](https://github.com/Tamago-chan/Hello-World) My very first repo.
* [**forum-project**](https://github.com/Tamago-chan/forum-project) The simple forum i'm working on
* [**tamago-chan.github.com**](https://github.com/Tamago-chan/tamago-chan.github.com) This page's repo

## Contat me
You can find me on github (obviously) @tamago-chan or email me at tamagochan99@gmail.com, i'm also often on IRC ([#phpmentoring @ freenode](http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=phpmentoring&uio=MTE9MjI2dd))
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
